{"tid":1973227,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"IMF: 中國肺炎令全球經濟衰退，但中國會成最大贏家","createTime":"2020-04-15T05:23:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T06:37:47.000Z","uid":290118,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5f0b29c2eead08712e6afc406bafbe2f460a7da3","tid":1973227,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T05:23:10.000Z","msg":"國際貨幣基金組織（IMF）認為，全球經濟表現將是自1930年代大蕭條以來最差。IMF形容，<del>新型</del>中國肺炎疫情令全球陷入災難，預料今年全球經濟將會收縮3%，收縮步伐亦是10年來最快。<br />\n<br />\n按照IMF的預測，美、英、日等主要經濟體今年將收縮5.9至6.5%，歐元區收縮7.5%，而中國就會有1.2%經濟增長；如果疫情在下半年受控，預計明年經濟可以增長5.8%。<br />\n<br />\nIMF發表的最新《環球金融穩定報告》指，在疫情衝擊下，中國金融狀況相對其他國家穩定，但個別環節金融壓力增加，例如中小型銀行資產負債表將進一步轉弱，大型發展商因銷售急速放緩，導致相關信貸及流動性風險上升等。"},{"pid":"7bd43c15dac5ed025e99f18e2c08c764f153670d","tid":1973227,"uid":260271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T05:25:11.000Z","msg":"on9，5.8%?<br />\n強国強係上來要58%都有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1953e5e4b331a6b59db89398ff13dd8c7d0e7d3d","tid":1973227,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T05:28:03.000Z","msg":"IMF又變咗做CMF？"},{"pid":"d7bf214afc3ef6d560e9634ac09092a0a383414b","tid":1973227,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:33:06.000Z","msg":"按照IMF的預測，<span style=\"color: red;\">美、英、日等主要經濟體今年將收縮5.9至6.5%</span>，<span style=\"color: blue;\">歐元區收縮7.5%</span>，<span style=\"color: green;\">而中國就會有1.2%經濟增長</span>；如果疫情在下半年受控，<span style=\"color: red;\">預計</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">明年經濟</span>可<span style=\"color: green;\">以增長5.8%。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=coH_Y0P3Owc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcoH_Y0P3Owc&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQOyReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=6650322f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=coH_Y0P3Owc</a>"},{"pid":"2af4b2b7eed5dee64e0645ebf9ca054db00a98e1","tid":1973227,"uid":41308,